        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'Open /RSK_03_Internal_Audit_Plan.docx in Word for Web. Using Copilot in Word, draft a new 2-page remediation acceleration memo that explains which divisions are furthest behind on remediation, which resource constraints are blocking progress, and the proposed 14-day sprint plan to close at least 6 High-rated findings before the Board Risk Committee. Use Edit with Copilot to insert a RAG table classifying each division\'s remediation status as On Track, At Risk, or Critical, and to add clear milestones for the sprint. Present as a Board-ready paper.'},
