        {'instr':'Open Outlook on the Web. Click **New email** and open the **Copilot pane** on the right. Paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Draft an internal email to all 11 divisional risk leads immediately after the Board Risk Committee session, summarising the key decisions on remediation acceleration, the expectations for divisions with more than 5 High-rated findings (Red status), and the rules for incident escalation until the next Committee meeting. Reference the ERM Framework and the Risk Appetite Statement for the updated thresholds. End with 3 bullet points titled "What you must do this fortnight". Use Coach my response to keep the tone firm and risk-governance aligned.'}
